DemoShot (console command)
==========================

Description
-----------

Takes a screenshot and saves it as a .[DEMO\_(file\_format).html DEMO] file.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

`demoshotÂ [Filename]`

Parameters
----------

-   [Filename] - Optional name for file suffix.

Notes
-----

If filename option is used this command will output a file with the following name:

`shot_<filename>.demo`

These demo shots can be benchmarked with the [TimeDemo\_(console\_command).html timeDemo] console command.


